headline: 3 Bank Stocks with Questionable Fundamentals
summary: Banks play a critical role in the financial system, providing everything from commercial loans to wealth management and payment processing services. But worries about an economic slowdown and potential credit deterioration have kept sentiment in check, and over the past six months, the banking industry’s 4.2% return has trailed the S&P 500 by 2.4 percentage points.
